      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1880&rangeEnd=1896"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_3_1106-1125",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1106-1125",
      "markText": "在官场上历练久了，敷衍的本事是第一等。",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1106&rangeEnd=1125",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1106&rangeEnd=1125"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_3_1358-1394",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1358-1394",
      "markText": "见人说人话，见鬼说鬼话，见了官场说官场上的话，见了生意人说生意场中的话。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1358&rangeEnd=1394",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1358&rangeEnd=1394"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_4_3265-3295",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3265-3295",
      "markText": "是个好些儿的，就去中进士做官给我看，不要在我们家里混闲饭吃。",
      "totalCount": 646,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3265&rangeEnd=3295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3265&rangeEnd=3295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_4_2670-2703",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2670-2703",
      "markText": "拉了翰林就有官做。做了官就有钱赚，还要坐堂打人，出起门来，开锣喝道",
      "totalCount": 602,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2670&rangeEnd=2703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2670&rangeEnd=2703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_6_2576-2650",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2576-2650",
      "markText": "都老爷无奈，只好拿信给他。胡理也不吃烟，不吃茶，取了信一直去找钱典史。告诉他，替他垫了一百两银子，起先徐家里还不肯写，后来看我面上却不过，他才写的。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2576&rangeEnd=2650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2576&rangeEnd=2650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_3_849-873",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "849-873",
      "markText": "吏治之坏，由于操守不廉；操守不廉，由于奢侈无度。",
      "totalCount": 464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=849&rangeEnd=873",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=849&rangeEnd=873"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_4_3040-3135",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3040-3135",
      "markText": "：“混帐东西！我今儿一番好意，拿好话教导与你，你倒教训起我来了！问问你爸爸：请了我来，是叫我管你的呢，还是叫你管我的？学生都要管起师傅来，这还了得！这个馆不能处了！一定要辞馆，一定要辞馆！”",
      "totalCount": 440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3040&rangeEnd=3135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3040&rangeEnd=3135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_3_589-616",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "589-616",
      "markText": "梦里所到的地方，竟是一片康庄大道，马来车往，络绎不绝。",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=589&rangeEnd=616",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=589&rangeEnd=616"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_5_2480-2502",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2480-2502",
      "markText": "做官不论大小，总要像他这样，这官才不算白做。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2502",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2502"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_5_2220-2303",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2220-2303",
      "markText": "谁知他到了此时，不但他爷爷临走嘱咐他到城之后，见了王乡绅替他问好的话，一句说不上来，连听了王乡绅的话，也不知如何回答。面孔涨得通红，嘴里吱吱了半天，才回了个“好”字。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169108&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2303",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2403238071800cd42403526?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25169108_9_1922-1982",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1922-1982",
      "markText": "到了年底，倒是那刑名仗着此事出了把力，写封信来问王梦梅借五百银子过年，王梦梅应酬了他二百两，才把这事过去。此是后话不题。",
